OL,4,CSchool catch-up tsar resigns over lack
OL,5,Cof funding
OL,6, The education recovery commissioner for
OL,7, England, Sir Kevan Collins, has
OL,8, resigned in a row over the lack of
OL,9, "credible" Covid catch-up funding.
OL,11,FSir Kevan took on the role as catch-up
OL,12,Ftsar in February to develop a long-term
OL,13,Fplan to help pupils make up for lost
OL,14,Flearning during the pandemic.
OL,16,FBut on Wednesday he stepped down saying
OL,17,Fthe government's funding for the plan
OL,18,F"falls far short of what is needed".
OL,20,FHead teachers labelled the #1.4bn cash
OL,21,Fover three years as a "damp squib".
